name: WestJet Cargo To Fly 737-800 Freighters!
description:
On June 23rd, 2021, Calgary-based WestJet announced that they’re joining the dedicated freighter market, by launching cargo-only flights with some converted Boeing 737-800s!

I don't think I ever expected to see that, so this is some very interesting news! Can't wait to see the first one sometime next year!
